Class ChapmanUser

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.chapman.operationsaferide.User

    Created by Melissa LeBlanc on 4/5/16.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Melissa LeBlanc
    See Also:
    User}. This class inherits from the User class, which contains one string attribute called name. It contains the attributes: chapmanID, numGuests, state, type,pickupLocation, and dropoffLocation. It represents the user side of the OperationSafeRide app and has various associated functions including sending a ride request (as an email) to Public Safety.
